                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                  <h2 class="text-[#111518] text-base font-bold leading-tight">Supportive Community
                  </h2>
                  <p class="text-[#637c88] text-sm font-normal leading-normal">
                    Join our community of pet lovers for tips, advice, and support throughout your
